description: Gobble, gobble, it’s TURKEY TIME! We couldn’t go away for the long weekend without telling you exactly what WE’RE thankful for! Here’s a hint, one of them is you! Trader Joe’s is another, but tune in to hear the rest! And have a HAPPY THANKSGIVING! [www.hungry-girl.com/foodcast](www.hungry-girl.com/foodcast)
